                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "The complete No.JS framework is approximately 14 KB gzipped. This includes all features: reactivity, routing, data fetching, i18n, animations, drag & drop, and form validation. Compare that to React (44 KB) + React DOM (130 KB).",
