                          "fill": "#64748B",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "No. No.JS works directly in the browser with a single script tag. There's no compilation, transpilation, or bundling required. Just include the CDN link and start building. Your deployment is as simple as uploading HTML files.",
